name: Gather Community Plant #020 - Waxhead
description:
The Gather Community Plant Collection features works from Tezos artists and their rendition of the GatherArt plant. The plant signifies beginnings, growth, eco friendliness, and the concept of nurturing what we love.

Waxhead is a street artist, painter, and sculptor turned digital artist who has found a home in the Tezos ecosystems of HEN & FxHash. They have a distinct style that stems from a love of graffiti.

"I was greatly influenced by street art and graffiti growing up, artists I saw painting on the freights like Labrona, Troy Lovegates (Other) and Swamp Donkey. They drew more characters instead of letters which influenced me greatly." - Waxhead
